 "long_description": "[TEL] NGDC non-cluster systemd fluentbit-logs down is Triggered\n\nTIP Runbook URL: https://pages.github.ibm.com/cloudlab/internal-docs/tel_host_logging_agent_troubleshooting.html\nTIP Short Description: NGDC non-cluster systemd fluentbit-logs is down on host hw-automation-vm-ca-mon for the past hour\nTIP Situation: NGDC non-cluster systemd fluentbit-logs down\nTIP Console: toc\nTIP CRN: crn:v1:::is-platform-integration:::mgmt:host:hw-automation-vm-ca-mon\n\nEvent Generated:\n\nSeverity:         Medium\nMetric:\n    min by (host_hostname, agent_tag_cluster, agent_tag_cluster_type) ( sysdig_program_up{program_cmd_line=\"/usr/bin/fluent-bit -c /etc/fluent-bit/conf/ops-logs/fluent.conf\", agent_tag_cluster=\"\"} or present_over_time(sysdig_program_up{program_cmd_line=\"/usr/bin/fluent-bit -c /etc/fluent-bit/conf/ops-logs/fluent.conf\", agent_tag_cluster=\"\"}[7d]) * 0 ) == 0 = 0\nSegment:\n    agent_tag_cluster_type = 'mgmt' and host_hostname = 'hw-automation-vm-ca-mon'\n\nTime:             12/10/2025 02:00 AM UTC\nState:            Triggered\nNotification URL: https://us-east.monitoring.cloud.ibm.com:443/api/oauth/openid/IBM/2c4a1985f9d5c10bd4842d2d3989088e/675be9de-53de-4e9b-b61e-5e297333a334?redirectRoute=%2Fevents%2Fnotifications%2Fl%3A2419200%2F44074923%2Fdetails\n\n------\n\nTriggered by Alert:\n\nType:         Prometheus\nName:         [TEL] NGDC non-cluster systemd fluentbit-logs down\nDescription:  NGDC non-cluster systemd fluentbit-logs process is down on the reported host. This alert's definition needs to be different from the norm. When a process stops running on a machine, data disappears in Sysdig. So special multiplication is needed so that we have zero values available in the 'no data' gaps. Also, we are using a 7d interval in the condition to provide us with zeros instead of 'no data' for an extended period of time to keep Sysdig from auto-resolving the alert and to keep the SNOW incident open long enough for our team to deal with the problem.\nTeam:         Monitor Operations\nScope:\n    Everywhere\nAlert When:   min by (host_hostname, agent_tag_cluster, agent_tag_cluster_type) ( sysdig_program_up{program_cmd_line=\"/usr/bin/fluent-bit -c /etc/fluent-bit/conf/ops-logs/fluent.conf\", agent_tag_cluster=\"\"} or present_over_time(sysdig_program_up{program_cmd_line=\"/usr/bin/fluent-bit -c /etc/fluent-bit/conf/ops-logs/fluent.conf\", agent_tag_cluster=\"\"}[7d]) * 0 ) == 0\nDuration: 1 h\nAlert URL:    https://us-east.monitoring.cloud.ibm.com:443/api/oauth/openid/IBM/2c4a1985f9d5c10bd4842d2d3989088e/675be9de-53de-4e9b-b61e-5e297333a334?redirectRoute=%2Falerts%2Frules%3FalertId%3D546995",
